Ben Smith is the former UC Davis campus coordinator for CalPIRG. He lived the Sunwise Coop. He was a champion runner with golden locks, although on occasion he cut those locks. Over winter break 2005 he was promoted to a statewide CalPIRG coordinator, which also includes Reno. However, he will mostly be focusing on organizing the Los Angelesarea community colleges, thus he now resides in Los Angeles.
